# S03-T08: HUD Presets

## Objective
Provide canned HUD configurations: COMBAT / NAV / DIAGNOSTICS / MINIMAL.

## Acceptance Criteria
- `useLayoutStore.preset` switchable via `setPreset(id)`.
- Preset definitions in `src/features/hud/presets/presets.ts`:
  - COMBAT: radar, target overlay, crosshair, attitude
  - NAV: compass, ALT/SPD, map (future)
  - DIAGNOSTICS: latency, stream stats, telemetry inspector
  - MINIMAL: only crosshair + critical alerts
- Preset switch fades slots (200ms) without unmounting AppShell.

## Steps
1. Define `HudPreset` type and preset records.
2. Wire `setPreset` to slot visibility map.
3. Add preset selector to top-bar (compact 4-button group).
4. Persist last preset to localStorage.

## Invariants
- Preset switch never causes video remount.
- Animations strict ease-out per UI_REGULATION.
- Default preset = COMBAT.
